{"tid":1508823,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"＜尋人＞幫朋友搵返823人鏈活動企佢隔離個巴打","createTime":"2019-08-26T15:37:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T05:49:24.000Z","uid":313302,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c2002fec4d325a567546877745fa8106882f607d","tid":1508823,"uid":313302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T15:37:02.000Z","msg":"(代朋友尋人)<br />\n<br />\n我有位絲打朋友參加左823號人鏈活動，想同企佢隔離嘅巴打相認，當晚佢地企係葵涌健全街同禾塘咀街交界，近健全街紅綠燈位。果位巴打著黑色champion短袖tee黑色長褲黑色波鞋，左手有戴錶，戴普通外科口罩。<br />\n<br />\n如果大家可以提供線索，甚至你就係本人，歡迎你同我聯絡，我會代我朋友同你聯絡，多謝大家幫助！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望大家唔好屌我呢個時間搵人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人加油！五大訴求，缺一不可！"},{"pid":"41883026889ee1f102aca402c2b2b3af4bc842cc","tid":1508823,"uid":286964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T15:37:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">求幫推</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最新post 睇得清楚d + 加左明天有義士再審係頂！</span></span>(極正經)(請推至長期置頂)被捕義士進程，一個也不能少不只是口號！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1508237\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1508237</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"aa96523545f625d1452322338f9016f0eb2f0df8","tid":1508823,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T15:41:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9hjf7rg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9hjf7rg.gif&h=994c84f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsYlFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=c026a546\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me